{"tid":1728630,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[文宣] 11.24 為區選打響頭炮！","createTime":"2019-11-17T03:11:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T09:59:27.000Z","uid":209415,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ae61763cd181d6ada2d7fda434b1881c84846278","tid":1728630,"uid":209415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T03:11:54.000Z","msg":"啲廢老一係就俾屋企送晒去<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>旅行</strong></span>，一係就唔投票/為蛇齋餅糭投建制派！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但我地都唔可以放過佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 某啲區嘅民賤聯拉票好撚落力，民主派呢？！所以我地自己行動啦！<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">洗爆佢地腦</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n重點係好撚多過左18歲嘅後生仔為左翻工！我屌晒你地咁多個老母啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />等你放得工翻嚟個投票隨時腰斬你地含晒撚啦！所以send埋俾你身邊嘅朋友，轟炸佢地！<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>每一票我地都好珍惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span> <br />\n<br />\n個日好早啲起身，可能手足們都未訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />帶埋<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">身份證</span>去投票喇！<br />\n<br />\n<strong>光復香港 時代革命</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ws12F6T.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWs12F6T.png&h=8db276e4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2r5fgFe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2r5fgFe.jpg&h=f7fd2b3a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bbcc0aa192ae78016f9be10bc90cf62c391f71b6","tid":1728630,"uid":209415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T03:12:40.000Z","msg":"自推1"},{"pid":"ab4a6efa73ebc37f3befc4f67b2cdf9d41217287","tid":1728630,"uid":209415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T03:12:50.000Z","msg":"自推2"},{"pid":"c17ab5f463f97d3f32317b37e815403c957ccbd6","tid":1728630,"uid":199709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T03:12:54.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">今日呀!!!!</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n166n5e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn166n5e.jpg&h=c05f57e1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n主題📜：東歐巨變30周年集會<br />\n日期📅：17/11/2019<br />\n時間🕐：1900～2130<br />\n地點⛩：中環愛丁堡廣場<br />\n備注🌟：已獲得不反對通知書<br />\n<br />\n特別事項⚠️<br />\n👉🏻1400 ～ 1700砌牆<br />\n👉🏻招募義工一齊砌出和裝飾柏林圍牆<br />\n👉🏻2120推倒極權暴政的鐵幕<br />\n👉🏻與30年前同步，東德開放畀人民入西德，寓意希望自由民主歸回人民<br />\n👉🏻同時招募糾察幫忙維持集會秩序<br />\n👉🏻義工和糾察聯絡： @sdontstandforshit<br />\n<br />\n鐵 幕 倒 下🧱極 權 必 亡☠️<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1723763/\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1723763/</a> <br />\n公海 Link : <a href=\"http://t.me/easterneurope1989\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Feasterneurope1989&d=PiwLpsDni%2BEQUOLZDbBUz1T2VSzVBU3ss%2BeERvjOeOk%3D&h=6a712dc1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/easterneurope1989</a>"},{"pid":"0e876660c7ebffd70a40dee738ffe6948d41b37a","tid":1728630,"uid":209415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T03:13:01.000Z","msg":"自推3"},{"pid":"05d553a3b1845c96bda48546fafe767fa3e9de9e","tid":1728630,"uid":209415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T03:13:12.000Z","msg":"自推4"},{"pid":"e36a5173c3148a892e29e277c529ec41404c49a6","tid":1728630,"uid":209415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T03:13:23.000Z","msg":"自推5"},{"pid":"8928b69395b28d2b12b82c516fa77b82ca15bf08","tid":1728630,"uid":209415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T03:13:35.000Z","msg":"自推6"},{"pid":"14fb7dca45cc50a9560adb26f2a3dbf67195797a","tid":1728630,"uid":209415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2